;&shy;ch acid uric qua &Auml;ë&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng ti&aacute;&raquo;Éu. Th&aacute;&raquo;&copy; nh&Atilde;&not; l&Atilde;&nbsp; y&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u t&aacute;&raquo;ë m&Atilde;&acute;i tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng. Ph&aacute;&raquo;ï bi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t &aacute;&raquo;ü &Auml;ë&Atilde;&cent;y l&Atilde;&nbsp; vi&aacute;&raquo;ác &Auml;Én u&aacute;&raquo;ëng qu&Atilde;&iexcl; nhi&aacute;&raquo;Åu ch&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;m purin, c&Atilde;&sup3; trong da g&Atilde;&nbsp;, &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;ì l&Atilde;&sup2;ng, gi&Atilde;&sup2; heo, n&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;m b&Atilde;&sup2;, l&AElig;&deg;&AElig;&iexcl;n, c&Atilde;&iexcl; bi&aacute;&raquo;Én (&Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&middot;c bi&aacute;&raquo;át l&Atilde;&nbsp; c&Atilde;&iexcl; m&Atilde;&sup2;i, c&Atilde;&iexcl; n&aacute;&raquo;&yen;c), th&aacute;&raquo;ãt r&aacute;&raquo;&laquo;ng (&Auml;ëa s&aacute;&raquo;ë), l&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;p x&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;üng. Theo nhi&aacute;&raquo;Åu chuy&Atilde;&ordf;n gia dinh d&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&iexcl;ng, purin trong th&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c ph&aacute;&ordm;&copy;m kh&Atilde;&acute;ng tr&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;p g&Atilde;&cent;y h&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i, m&Atilde;&nbsp; ch&aacute;&raquo;â tr&aacute;&raquo;ü th&Atilde;&nbsp;nh &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;ôc ch&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t khi &Auml;Én k&Atilde;&uml;m v&aacute;&raquo;õi m&aacute;&raquo;&iexcl; &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;ông v&aacute;&ordm;&shy;t. C&AElig;&iexcl; ch&aacute;&ordm;&iquest; g&Atilde;&cent;y b&aacute;&raquo;ánh &aacute;&raquo;ü &Auml;ë&Atilde;&cent;y l&Atilde;&nbsp; ch&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t b&Atilde;&copy;o ng&Auml;Én c&aacute;&ordm;&pound;n quy tr&Atilde;&not;nh b&Atilde;&nbsp;i ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t acid uric qua &Auml;ë&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng ti&aacute;&raquo;Éu.\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi ph&Atilde;&cent;n t&Atilde;&shy;ch th&Atilde;&sup3;i quen c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a nh&aacute;&raquo;&macr;ng ng&AElig;&deg