;&ordm;&pound;i &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&pound;m b&aacute;&ordm;&pound;o, d&Atilde;&sup1;ng &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;&sect; li&aacute;&raquo;Åu &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;É ti&Atilde;&ordf;u di&aacute;&raquo;át vi khu&aacute;&ordm;&copy;n, ch&aacute;&raquo;&copy; kh&Atilde;&acute;ng th&aacute;&raquo;É u&aacute;&raquo;ëng n&aacute;&raquo;&shy;a ch&aacute;&raquo;&laquo;ng\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;color:#008C00;font-weight:bold&quot;&gt;T&Atilde;&sup1;y ti&aacute;&raquo;án d&Atilde;&sup1;ng thu&aacute;&raquo;ëc!&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Theo m&aacute;&raquo;ôt nghi&Atilde;&ordf;n c&aacute;&raquo;&copy;u c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a BV Nhi Trung &AElig;&deg;&AElig;&iexcl;ng, c&Atilde;&sup3; t&aacute;&raquo;õi 44% b&Atilde;&nbsp; m&aacute;&ordm;&sup1; t&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; mua thu&aacute;&raquo;ëc cho con u&aacute;&raquo;ëng m&Atilde;&nbsp; kh&Atilde;&acute;ng c&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n k&Atilde;&ordf; &Auml;ë&AElig;&iexcl;n c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a b&Atilde;&iexcl;c s&Auml;&copy;. Vi&aacute;&raquo;ác t&Atilde;&sup1;y ti&aacute;&raquo;án d&Atilde;&sup1;ng thu&aacute;&raquo;ëc khi ch&AElig;&deg;a c&Atilde;&sup3; ch&aacute;&raquo;â &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;ãnh l&Atilde;&nbsp; r&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t nguy hi&aacute;&raquo;Ém, g&Atilde;&cent;y h&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i cho s&aacute;&raquo;&copy;c kh&aacute;&raquo;èe c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a tr&aacute;&ordm;&raquo;.\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Theo PGS.TS Nguy&aacute;&raquo;Ön Ti&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n D&Aring;&copy;ng, &Auml;ë&Atilde;&cent;y l&Atilde;&nbsp; m&aacute;&raquo;ôt sai l&aacute;&ordm;&sect;m r&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t &Auml;ë&Atilde;&iexcl;ng tr&Atilde;&iexcl;ch c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a c&Atilde;&iexcl;c b&Atilde;&nbsp; m&aacute;&ordm;&sup1;. V&Atilde;&not; vi&aacute;&raquo;ác t&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn; ch&aacute;&raquo;&macr;a cho con, ch&aacute;&raquo;&macr;a theo &Auml;ë&AElig;&iexcl;n c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a b&Atilde;&copy; kh&Atilde;&iexcl;c&acirc;Ä&brvbar; khi&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n nhi&aacute;&raquo;Åu tr&aacute;&ordm;&raquo; b&aacute;&raquo;ã bi&a