&ordf;n t&aacute;&ordm;&macr;c &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u ti&Atilde;&ordf;n c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a vi&aacute;&raquo;ác d&Atilde;&sup1;ng kh&Atilde;&iexcl;ng sinh, &Auml;ë&Atilde;&sup3; l&Atilde;&nbsp; ch&aacute;&raquo;â d&Atilde;&sup1;ng kh&Atilde;&iexcl;ng sinh khi c&Atilde;&sup3; nhi&aacute;&raquo;Öm khu&aacute;&ordm;&copy;n (vi khu&aacute;&ordm;&copy;n). Th&aacute;&raquo;ëng k&Atilde;&ordf; t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i M&aacute;&raquo;&sup1;, t&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; c&Atilde;&iexcl;c tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng h&aacute;&raquo;&pound;p d&Atilde;&sup1;ng kh&Atilde;&iexcl;ng sinh trong nhi&aacute;&raquo;Öm khu&aacute;&ordm;&copy;n h&Atilde;&acute; h&aacute;&ordm;&yen;p tr&Atilde;&ordf;n, s&aacute;&raquo;ë &Auml;ë&AElig;&iexcl;n &Auml;ë&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;c k&Atilde;&ordf; kh&Atilde;&iexcl;ng sinh so v&aacute;&raquo;õi b&aacute;&raquo;ánh nh&Atilde;&cent;n c&Atilde;&sup3; b&aacute;&ordm;&plusmn;ng ch&aacute;&raquo;&copy;ng nhi&aacute;&raquo;Öm vi khu&aacute;&ordm;&copy;n th&Atilde;&not; l&aacute;&raquo;õn h&AElig;&iexcl;n r&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t nhi&aacute;&raquo;Åu. T&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i Vi&aacute;&raquo;át Nam, th&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c tr&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;ng c&Aring;&copy;ng nh&AElig;&deg; v&aacute;&ordm;&shy;y.\r\n&lt;p&gt;- M&aacute;&raquo;ôt nghi&Atilde;&ordf;n c&aacute;&raquo;&copy;u do BV B&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;ch Mai, H&Atilde;&nbsp; N&aacute;&raquo;ôi ph&aacute;&raquo;ëi h&aacute;&raquo;&pound;p tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng &Auml;êH Harvard th&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c hi&aacute;&raquo;án t&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;i 16 huy&aacute;&raquo;án &aacute;&raquo;ü Vi&aacute;&raquo;át Nam cho th&aacute;&ordm;&yen;y, c&Atilde;&sup3; &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n 97 &acirc;Äì 99% c&Atilde;&iexcl;c ch&Atilde;&iexcl;u d&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;õi 5 tu&aacute;&raquo;ïi &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;n c&Atilde;&iexcl;c ph&Atilde;&sup2;ng kh&Atilde;&iexcl;m v&Atilde;&not; ho, s&aacute;&raquo;ët, ch&aacute;&ordm;&pound;y n&AElig;&de