;&sup3;ng m&aacute;&ordm;&middot;t, c&Auml;Éng ng&aacute;&raquo;&plusmn;c, bu&aacute;&raquo;ìn n&Atilde;&acute;n &acirc;Ä&brvbar; C&Atilde;&iexcl;c tri&aacute;&raquo;áu ch&aacute;&raquo;&copy;ng n&Atilde;&nbsp;y th&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng tho&Atilde;&iexcl;ng qua hay gi&aacute;&ordm;&pound;m &Auml;ëi theo th&aacute;&raquo;ùi gian.&lt;/br&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color:#008C00;font-weight:bold&quot;&gt;&AElig;&macr;u &Auml;ëi&aacute;&raquo;Ém c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a Implanon&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/br&gt;\r\n&Auml;ê&aacute;&raquo;ëi t&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;&pound;ng s&aacute;&raquo;&shy; d&aacute;&raquo;&yen;ng c&aacute;&raquo;&sect;a Implanon l&Atilde;&nbsp; r&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t r&aacute;&raquo;ông. C&Atilde;&iexcl;c b&Atilde;&nbsp; m&aacute;&ordm;&sup1; &Auml;ëang cho con b&Atilde;&ordm;, ph&aacute;&raquo;&yen; n&aacute;&raquo;&macr; tr&Atilde;&ordf;n 40 tu&aacute;&raquo;ïi, ng&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùi c&Atilde;&sup3; u x&AElig;&iexcl; t&aacute;&raquo;&shy; cung c&Atilde;&sup3; th&aacute;&raquo;É s&aacute;&raquo;&shy; d&aacute;&raquo;&yen;ng Implanon an to&Atilde;&nbsp;n. C&Atilde;&iexcl;c b&Atilde;&nbsp; m&aacute;&ordm;&sup1; t&aacute;&raquo;ët nh&aacute;&ordm;&yen;t n&Atilde;&ordf;n &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;&pound;i tr&aacute;&ordm;&raquo; h&AElig;&iexcl;n 6 tu&aacute;&ordm;&sect;n tu&aacute;&raquo;ïi m&aacute;&raquo;õi b&aacute;&ordm;&macr;t &Auml;ë&aacute;&ordm;&sect;u s&aacute;&raquo;&shy; d&aacute;&raquo;&yen;ng que c&aacute;&ordm;&yen;y n&Atilde;&nbsp;y.&lt;/br&gt;\r\nC&Atilde;&iexcl;c tr&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng h&aacute;&raquo;&pound;p c&Atilde;&sup3; y&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;u t&aacute;&raquo;ë nguy c&AElig;&iexcl; cho tim m&aacute;&ordm;&iexcl;ch nh&AElig;&deg; h&Atilde;&ordm;t thu&aacute;&raquo;ëc l&Atilde;&iexcl;, b&Atilde;&copy;o ph&Atilde;&not;, ti&aacute;&raquo;Éu &Auml;ë&AElig;&deg;&aacute;&raquo;ùng hay c&aacute;&ordm;&pound; b&aacute;&raquo;ánh nh&Atilde;&cent;n cao huy&aacute;&ordm;&iquest;t &Atilde;&iexcl;p &Auml;ë&aacute;&raquo;Å